<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <$- include('./partials/head') $>
</head>
<body >
  <$- include('./partials/navbar') $>
  <div class="center-align">
    <div class="container page-btn">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="gameRules cyan darken-2 col s12 m12 white-text">
          Welcome to SnapThis, a photo scavenger hunt! We've outlined the general rules for the host and for players below. Enjoy!
        </div>
        <div class="col s12 m6 l4">
          <div class="center promo">
            <h4 class="card-title">Host</h4>
            <i class="large material-icons">present_to_all</i>
            <h6 class="card-content">Create a game and share your secret code with your friends. They can join your game from anywhere in the world!</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col s12 m6 l4">
          <div class="center promo">
            <h4 class="card-title">Host</h4>
            <i class="large material-icons">playlist_add</i>
            <h6 class="card-content">Easily add tasks to your scavenger hunt before you start the game. Add as many as you like, but beware, because that means you'll have to...</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col s12 m6 l4">
          <div class="center promo">
            <h4 class="card-title">Host</h4>
            <i class="large material-icons">done_all</i>
            <h6 class="card-content">Rate the pictures that players submit! Whenever you see a photo, you'll get to either approve or reject it for the game that you're hosting. Be as judgmental as you like!</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col s12 m6 l4">
          <div class="center promo">
            <h4 class="card-title">Player</h4>
            <i class="large material-icons">person_pin</i>
            <h6 class="card-content">Join a scavenger hunt using the secret code given to you by the host.</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col s12 m6 l4">
          <div class="center promo">
            <h4 class="card-title">Player</h4>
            <i class="large material-icons">queue</i>
            <h6 class="card-content">Read the task, snap a shot, and upload it via image url to your game.</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col s12 m6 l4">
          <div class="center promo">
            <h4 class="card-title">Player</h4>
            <i class="large material-icons">loop</i>
            <h6 class="card-content">If the host rejects your picture, try again. If the host accepts your picture, move onto the next task and repeat!</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


      <$ if (user && !user.currentGame) { $>

        <div class="card choice-btn">
          <div class="row">
            <form id="create-game" action="/api/games" method="post">
              <button type="submit" class="waves-effect waves-light btn-large">Create Game</button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <form action="/api/games/join" method="post">
              <label for="search">Join A Game</label>
              <input id="join-game" type="text" name="gameId" placeholder="enter secret code">
              <input type="submit" value="join" class="waves-effect waves-light btn-large">
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>

      <$ } else if(user && user.currentGame) { $>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col s12 m8 push-m2">
          <div class="card choice-btn">
            <a href="/api/games/<$= user.currentGame $>" class="waves-effect waves-light btn-large">Continue Game</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col s12 m8 push-m2">
          <div class="card choice-btn">
            <a href="/users/leavegame" class="waves-effect waves-light btn-large">Leave Game</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

        <$ } $>

        <h1>Meet the Team</h1>
        <div class="row about-us">
          <div class="col s12 m6">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-image">
                <img src="../images/AJ_1503434.jpg">
                <span class="card-title">A.J. Almaguer</span>
              </div>
              <div class="card-content">
                <p>Back-End</p>
              </div>
              <div class="card-action">
                <a href="https://github.com/ajalmaguer" target="_blank">See A.J.'s GitHub profile</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row about-us">
          <div class="col s12 m6">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-image">
                <img src="../images/Brigette_2372.jpg">
                <span class="card-title">Brigette Morando</span>
              </div>
              <div class="card-content">
                <p>Git Master</p>
              </div>
              <div class="card-action">
                <a href="https://github.com/bmorando" target="_blank">See Brigette's GitHub profile</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row about-us">
          <div class="col s12 m6">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-image">
                <img src="../images/Marcos_1265937.jpg">
                <span class="card-title">Marcos Felix</span>
              </div>
              <div class="card-content">
                <p>Front-End</p>
              </div>
              <div class="card-action">
                <a href="https://github.com/bmorando" target="_blank">See Marcos's GitHub profile</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row about-us">
          <div class="col s12 m6">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-image">
                <img src="../images/Victor_256726.jpg">
                <span class="card-title">Victor Tran</span>
              </div>
              <div class="card-content">
                <p>Bug Testing</p>
              </div>
              <div class="card-action">
                <a href="https://github.com/murtato" target="_blank">See Victor's GitHub profile</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
